Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是梦?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我的幻觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击法尼利亚的巨人\N让亚连的守城也陷入了一片火海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,我的预感再度成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人从空中攻击我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙让艾斯嘉科尼化身为龙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让我们逃走,独自一人离开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:01:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将巨人们引开…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你不快点逃的话,可是会被我追上的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧,我快要击中你了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风向乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又隐形了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我逮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是自愿当饵好让其他人脱逃,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌这种爱耍帅的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就不行了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想杀死他吗?迪兰度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该是要捉活他的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是跟他玩玩罢了,军师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟的刻印
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有火,看到火光了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看到装甲的残骸吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道,梵大人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,他们不会杀梵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说只有法尼利亚王\N才能够敔动艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会去救他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想还他这笔人情债
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这□气我吞不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要宰了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长,你打算怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩下多少人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我在内一共有7名士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对付那座浮游要塞正面攻击可能有点吃力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,得先掌握他们的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我可能有办法知道梵现在人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的守城会遭到攻击的事的确被你说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那并不是什么巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从小预感就蛮准的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…其实我自己也不懂是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是,我的那股能力越来越强了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算真是那样好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这终究是我们骑士的职责所在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能谅解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就请你测试一下我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经派了讨伐队过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙是回不了国的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不需要继续在这里躲躲藏藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能太过大意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等他们的回报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是那么小心翼翼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,这下子我们的未来就能高枕无忧了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点将里头的武士拖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把它破坏掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能让你这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得等到我查明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它为什么会危害到我们的未来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我找出原因之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,他就是新任的法尼利亚王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓得我浑身冒冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小妞真的能知道老大的过去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:07:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IL Pazzo,愚者的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我中心的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视于常理的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲的个性就展现在这张卡片上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道阴影覆盖了你的家人导致关系崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人的分离
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,她说对了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为老大不喜欢说他的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的妹妹之所以会失踪还有母亲的病逝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是因为他父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是说了不该说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我一定要取得亚连的信任才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管了,说就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IL Giudizio,审判的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久的将来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有机会和你的父亲重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你执着于过去无法将心中的仇恨给…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张卡片是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你及格了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把梵的所在地找出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会唱法尼利亚的民谣?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我去拿我的人型装甲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这种恐吓就能让寨巴哈士兵屈服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是无法离开这座浮游要塞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其要成为你们的道具苟活下去,还不如…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以浪费生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样子真的会有办法知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有办法的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有十年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄并不是逃避了继承王位的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是与龙战斗而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未背朝敌人奋战至最后一刻才牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么你会在寨巴哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要将法尼利亚烧成废墟?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我一起去见寨巴哈皇帝多伦卡喀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一同目睹崭新的未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用,请让我继续
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是…要是有什么他接触过的东西就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么做才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心地…想着他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是"漂流大地"的聚集地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流大地?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是跟这艘船一样是漂浮的岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对喔,那里是那个浮游要塞的最佳藏匿处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙就是会威胁到寨巴哈帝国未来的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个古董罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,弗肯那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有办法操纵它呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现浮游要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加热浮游石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除浮力,一□气攻入要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮力减少至20
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收帆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停机库发生原因不明的爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军来袭,就在正上方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下锚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮力恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,松开锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收起推进器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后方系留船锚发射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,登陆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟发生了什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.43,0:16:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝藏…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度大人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若没有迪兰度大人的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快分头去找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好,你可别乱动喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得过去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去通知梵才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来救我的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离5公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,应该有6公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟想要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跳过去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的跳远纪录是5公尺40
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能跳得过去的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相隔那么远耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去的话会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会摔烂的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪…怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快,我得快点去通知他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,后面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我早该宰了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的不得了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,撒退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯,准备撒退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟们,作战结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然将我这张俊美的脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亚高速船起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石能量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械输出动力为零
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你迟早会来到我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:20:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来是想救你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果反倒是你们救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这全都是托她的福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右满舵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到阿斯多利亚的都城"帕拉斯"去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:22:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找确吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谋略之都
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:57.87,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:06.32,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:13.95,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的门扉即将开启　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:20.10,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过这令人兴奋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:22.46,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:27.47,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃烧般的神秘双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:31.31,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真无邪的笑容让我倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:35.11,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深处的暗示只传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:39.12,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了无止尽的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.18,0:22:42.62,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心的鼓动无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:50.09,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想带着你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:57.86,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:06.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:13.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:20.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:22.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:27.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:31.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:35.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:39.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.18,0:22:42.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:50.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい


